descriptionHtml:
First of all i would like to THANK nanahane for making this mod...

That\'s right... this is not my mod...
I only added new voices... If you like it please don\'t forget to endorse :)

also try my other upload Anime Voice Shout
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24469

If you like it please don\'t forget to endorse :)

Watch the video here: http://youtu.be/X-f0_BIm7NM

You hear the voices of the following events.
- Discover new place
- 25% or less health of the player
- 50% or less health of the player
- Get the Dragon Soul
- Start combat
- Kill enemy

as you notice i removed some of the events (skill up, spell cast) because it\'s too noisy if you level up fast and keeps on casting... but I left the folder empty just in case you want to add something to it...

Once again thanks to nanahane for making the mod...
author: kyo92tricks
